title: The Fox 001 (2013) (digital) (Son of Ultron-Empire)
description:
CBR | English | 

The Fox #1
Written by Dean Haspiel and Mark Waid
Art by Dean Haspiel
Colours by Allen Passalaqua

New Red Circle Series! From the world of the New Crusaders, comes the fantastic debut of the high-flying FOX! When photojournalist Paul Patton, Jr. donned a super hero costume, he thought it would be a quick way to make some news-now the strange and unusual just can't help but be drawn to the freak-magnetism of the fabulous fighting FOX! While working on a puff-piece at the Red Circle Gazette, an evil truth about social media mogul Lucy Fur is discovered, bringing Paul face-to-face with a criminal kingpin!
